sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Prospect
    participant Chat as ChatUI
    participant API as /api/chat
    participant Claude as Claude claude-sonnet-4-6
    participant DB as Supabase

    Note over U,DB: Phase 1 — Lead Capture
    U->>Chat: "Hi, I want to explore insurance options"
    Chat->>API: POST {message, leadId: null}
    API->>DB: create lead (status: chatting)
    API->>Claude: system prompt + user message
    Claude-->>API: "Hi! I'm Priya from SecureLife. Could you share your name?"
    API->>DB: save assistant message
    API-->>Chat: stream response
    Chat-->>U: display reply

    U->>Chat: "My name is Rahul, I'm 34, married with 2 kids"
    Chat->>API: POST {message, leadId}
    API->>Claude: full conversation history
    Claude-->>API: reply + LEAD_DATA:{name,age,family_size}
    API->>DB: upsert lead fields, save messages
    API-->>Chat: stream response

    Note over U,DB: Phase 2 — Qualification & Handoff
    U->>Chat: finishes qualification questions
    API->>DB: update lead status → qualified
    API->>DB: update score (0–100)
    Chat-->>U: "Please upload your existing policy documents"
    API->>DB: update status → awaiting_docs

    Note over U,DB: Phase 3 — Document Processing
    U->>Chat: uploads PDF
    Chat->>API: POST /api/documents {file, leadId}
    API->>DB: create document record (status: processing)
    API->>API: pdf-parse extracts raw text
    API->>Claude: extraction prompt + raw text
    Claude-->>API: structured JSON {policy_type, sum_insured, ...}
    API->>DB: save extracted_data
    API->>DB: update document status → extracted
    API->>DB: update lead status → processing

    Note over U,DB: Phase 4 — Analysis Generation
    API->>DB: fetch lead profile + all extracted_data
    API->>Claude: analysis prompt + lead context
    Claude-->>API: {coverage_gaps, savings, risk_flags, recommendation}
    API->>DB: save analysis
    API->>DB: update lead status → completed
    API-->>Chat: notify dashboard
